  "title": "A Meeting with Sabbath on Etti IV",
  "summary": "At the Imperial Embassy on Etti IV, Corporate Sector Authority official Simone Drake arrives -- in place of the busy Executive Officer Dillon -- to meet the cloaked Imperial Sabbath in the embassy conference chamber. Sabbath, disappointed that Dillon could not attend, presses for the captured General Han Solo to be transferred to the Imperial Star Destroyer Vanguard so he can stand trial for war crimes against the Empire, warning that Solo's presence on the planet is bound to be leaked. Simone firmly declines, insisting the CSA will keep Solo in its own secured custody to face charges for crimes against the Authority, a position she shares with Dillon. Sabbath, unconvinced and noting that the decision is ultimately not hers, says he will take the matter up with Dillon directly. Simone agrees to find out when Dillon is available and excuses herself, leaving the embassy.",
